headline: Fortinet (NasdaqGS:FTNT) Announces Partnership With Liquid Networx For Enhanced Data Security
summary: Fortinet (NasdaqGS:FTNT) has seen a significant price increase of 15% over the past week, a notable shift that coincides with its recent partnership announcement with Liquid Networx. This collaboration focuses on deploying FortiDLP solutions to bolster data security for a major global retail enterprise. In a market that has risen 5% over the same period, Fortinet’s strong performance stands out, potentially driven by the strategic importance of this alliance in enhancing its cybersecurity...
